### 마이페이지에서 QR 티켓 조회
POST http://localhost:8080/api/qr-tickets
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "attendeeId": 1,
  "eventId": 1,
  "ticketId": 1,
  "reservationId": 1
}

### 비회원 QR 티켓 링크 통한 QR 티켓 조회
@token = n5fGh9fQ
GET http://localhost:8080/api/qr-tickets/{{token}}

### QR 티켓 새로고침 버튼 클릭 시 재발급
POST http://localhost:8080/api/qr-tickets/reissue
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "qrUrlToken": ""
}

### 행사 관리자 QR 티켓 리셋
POST http://localhost:8080/api/qr-tickets/admin/reissue
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "attendeeId": 1,
  "ticketNo": "EVT202408A-20250806-0001"
}

### QR 티켓 강제 재발급해 메일 발송
POST http://localhost:8080/api/qr-tickets/admin/reissue/send-email
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "attendeeId": 2,
  "ticketNo": "EVT202408A-20250806-0002"
}

### 회원 QR 스캔 입장
POST http://localhost:8080/api/qr-tickets/check-in/member/qr
Content-Type: application/json

{
 "reservationId": 1,
  "qrCode": "asdf"
}

### 회원 수동코드 스캔 입장
POST http://localhost:8080/api/qr-tickets/check-in/member/manual
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reservationId": 1,
  "manualCode": "asdf"
}

### 비회원 QR 스캔 입장
POST http://localhost:8080/api/qr-tickets/check-in/guest/qr
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "qrLinkToken": "dddd",
  "qrCode": "asdf"
}

### 비회원 수동코드 스캔 입장
POST http://localhost:8080/api/qr-tickets/check-in/guest/manual
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "qrLinkToken": "dddd",
  "manualCode": "asdf"
}